title: Episode 41: The Oscars, Sesame Street, and the decline of Western Civilization
description: Join Phil, Skye and Christian as they discuss the Harlem Shake and the decline of Western Civilization, plus a fascinating journey through gender issues in the Oscars, Sesame Street and beyond!
